A climb map, It has3 rooms

room 1: has the yoshi head and a working cannon to fire your friends to the top.

room 2: the second room after room , nothing special

room 3: the heli room, with fully controlable helicopters to play with and to give your frineds rides with.

map made by yoshi.fr 

the point in the map s to get to the heli room and to use teamwork to get everyone else there too. :)
